data.description: Very spacious and great split bedroom floor plan. Master bath has his/her closets and enclosed toilet area.  Seamless shower updated with tile and stone; jetted tub for a relaxing soaking bath. Bedrooms are carpeted and remainder of home has ceramic wood grained tile slats. Kitchen offers an abundance of cabinets; walk-in pantry surrounded with shelving.  Computer/recipe desk and walled chalkboard. Island has eating bar area. High ceilings throughout and accentuated with arched doorways and tray ceilings in the den dining area. Stay  warm near the ventless gas built-in fireplace. The backyard offers loads of entertainment with outdoor enclosed kitchen/man-cave. A unique compost is ready for spring planting.  Home is located on quite cul de sac.
